oneOf.description:

The target entity will be set as the damaged entity

The target entity will be set as the damaging entity

Otherwise, The target entity will be set as the damaging entity

oneOf.description: Damages the user or the target entity

Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for every entity in the range. 
The target entity will be set to the entity this trigger triggers for
Modifies the velocity of the user or target entity. Same as FLING
Cancels the event that triggered this effect
Sets the gliding mode of the user or target entity (works even if an Elytra is not equipped)

Acts like a trigger. 
Waits a duration of time before it triggers
Applies the potion effect to the user or target entity
Change the block at target entity for a duration of time, then change it back. Same as BLOCKENTITY

Shoot an arrow to the location of the target entity
Modifies an attribute owned by the user or target entity

Launches an entity. 
Mode `OTHER`: Launched in the direction of the target entity. 
Mode `SELF`: Launched in the direction the user is facing
Sends a chat message to the user or target player
Pick up the target entity and places it on the user's head
Repulse the target entity
Resizes the user or target entity (for slimes, magma cubes, and phantoms)
Smites the user or target entity. Same as LIGHTNING
Smites the user or target entity. Same as SMITE
Modifies the velocity of the user or target entity. Same as VELOCITY
Modifies a user defined variable
Gives the user or target entity an item
Scrambles the inventory of the user or target entity
Teleports the user or target entity a random distance

Shoots an entity from the user. 
Mode `SELF`: Shoots in the direction that the user is looking. 
Mode `OTHER`: Shoots at the target entity. 
Mode `LOCATION`: Shoots at the location
Plays a sound at the location or at the location of the user or target entity
Excecutes a list of commands
Applies an acceleration to the user or the target entity based on the direction the entity is looking

Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for the nearest entity in the radius. 
The target entity will be set as the nearest entity

Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for the target entity. 
The new target entity will be set as the source of the projectile if the old target entity is a projectile, otherwise the target entity will remain the same
Applies a velocity to the target entity in the direction that the user is looking as the direction
Sets the user or target entity on fire. Same as FIRE
Sets the user or target entity on fire. Same as IGNITE
If the user is a mob, sets the target of the user to the target entity
Swaps the position of the user and target entity

Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for every location in the cube around the user or target entity. 
The location will be set as the location the trigger triggers for
Replaces a block at the location for an amount of time. Retains the original block data
Spawns an entity at the location or the location of the user or target entity
Removes potion effects from the user or target entity
Teleports the user to the location or the location of the target entity

Acts like a trigger. 
Sends out a raytrace that collides with entities or blocks in the direction that the user or target entity is looking. 
The target entity will be set as the collided entity. 
The location will be set as the location of the collided block

Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for a number of times with a period and initial delay. 
Target items will be forwarded
Removes the user or target entity

Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers for the item in the slot. 
The item will be set to the item in the slot
Modifies the item amount

Acts like a trigger. 
The target entity will be set as the original user.
 the user will be set as the original target entity

Acts like a trigger. 
Triggers the location of the user or target entity after being offseted. 
The location will be set as the location the trigger triggers for
Applies bonemeal to the location or location of the user or target entity
Modifies the hunger value of the user or target entity
Make the user lose interest in the current target
Breaks surrounding blocks around a location recursively
Sends an action bar to the user or target entity
Modifies the user or target entity freezing ticks (ie. powdered snow effect)
Modifies the health of the user or target entity. Also rounds down to the nearest hitpoint/half a heart

Sets the ability for the creative flight. Alias for FLYING 

Modes: 
SELF: For the user;
OTHER: For the target entity.

Sets the ability for the creative flight. Alias for FLY 

Modes: 
SELF: For the user;
OTHER: For the target entity.
Modifies a furnace's burn time
Spawns particles

Only available if you have the SuperheroesPlusUltra plugin

Only available if you have the EnchantedBosses plugin

Spawns a boss that rides the user

Only available if you have the EnchantedBosses plugin
